Happy path: Create a Number category and place it on a page
Go to assessment and play with the attribute: try every possible entry and see how it reacts to it. Make sure the values are saved.
Look at the page with read-only permission.
Make it non-blanking and then disable encounter and make sure the value stays intact.
Go to Region Admin and make it a triggered category. (Make sure the attribute appears in the expand view)
Test the triggering action in Assessment.
Define an order template for the page with the number category
Use the Order template to apply the chages to a tab
Check the clinical profile details in Facility and ensure that the value of number attributes are displayed as "[attributeName]: [numerical value]"

